{"tid":2087323,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"健威花園兩房放盤減價近50萬求售","createTime":"2020-06-30T16:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T17:14:41.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b2dae252bd06cb119211b294efe7a6ea9df9cdeb","tid":2087323,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200630/photo/bkn-20200630134317076-0630_00842_001_01b.jpg?20200630185804\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200630%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200630134317076-0630_00842_001_01b.jpg%3F20200630185804&h=9ad497ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「港版國安法」今(30日)獲全國人大常委會全票通過，二手市場有業主劈價求售。世紀21日昇黃文龍稱，北角健威花園C座高層1室，實用面積446方呎，兩房間隔，望海景，原先叫價868萬港元放售，市場放盤已1個月，今早即時降價至820萬元，減幅約5.5%，每呎叫價約18,386元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200630/bkn-20200630134317076-0630_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200630%2Fbkn-20200630134317076-0630_00842_001.html&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=7a19f9fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200630/bkn-20200630134317076-0630_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ab9a635afdd0dc070c645ea7fc395fdd38dc5302","tid":2087323,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2dae252bd06cb119211b294efe7a6ea9df9cdeb","tid":2087323,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200630/photo/bkn-20200630134317076-0630_00842_001_01b.jpg?20200630185804\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200630%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200630134317076-0630_00842_001_01b.jpg%3F20200630185804&h=9ad497ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「港版國安法」今(30日)獲全國人大常委會全票通過，二手市場有業主劈價求售。世紀21日昇黃文龍稱，北角健威花園C座高層1室，實用面積446方呎，兩房間隔，望海景，原先叫價868萬港元放售，市場放盤